column30: I'm a passionate, outgoing person that loves to be involved in my community, mostly FilAm, and advocating for our people! I also love learning about American and Asian American history for that reason. In general I'm always looking for more ways to be informed in this political climate so I can be a better advocate for Filipinos and other minorities. Academically, I have a very low stress approach and it's worked out for me so far as I have a very good academic, family, work, and social balance.
